   <note type="physicalDetails">21 lines per page. Written in medium small naskh in black ink with use of red. European glazed paper with watermark. Foliation in pencil using Western numerals.
      No. "514" in Arabic script on a label pasted on the spine (vertical ; repeated on fol. 1a). No. "412" in Arabic script on a label pasted on the upper cover (repeated on fol. 1a)</note>
   <note type="physicalDetails">Collation: Paper ; fol. 92 ; 1-11⁸ 12⁴ ; catchword on the verso of each leaf</note>
